DarkMouse::
She got the transmission. "Oh no." She  opened her link. "KitKat, we 
got trouble coming."

::KitKat::
She heard DarkMouse. She shook her head, "Never a dull moment around 
here." She opened her link. "Apocalypse, go to DarkMouse and assist 
her. There might be someone there that you'll have to 'take care 
of'."
